## 🔐 Privacy & Security

### What Data is Stored Where?

| Data Type | Storage Location | You Control? |
|-----------|-----------------|--------------|
| Tasks | IndexedDB (50GB+) | ✅ Yes - 100% local |
| Calendar Events | IndexedDB (50GB+) | ✅ Yes - 100% local |
| Time Entries | IndexedDB (50GB+) | ✅ Yes - 100% local |
| Notes *(future)* | IndexedDB (50GB+) | ✅ Yes - 100% local |
| User Preferences | IndexedDB (50GB+) | ✅ Yes - 100% local |

### Privacy Guarantees

1. **No data EVER leaves your device** - Everything stays in your browser's IndexedDB, period.
2. **Zero tracking, zero analytics** - No telemetry, no Google Analytics, no Firebase Analytics.
3. **No account required** - Use the app anonymously with local storage.
4. **No cloud dependencies** - No Firebase, no Google Drive, no third-party services.
5. **Full data export always available** - Export to .brain files anytime (E2EE coming Q2 2026).
6. **Open source** - Audit the code yourself: [github.com/travisjneuman/system.knowledgebase](https://github.com/travisjneuman/system.knowledgebase)

### Local Backups (Your Control)

Want to backup or sync across devices?
- **Export .brain files** - Download encrypted backups to your computer
- **Auto-save to local folder** - Choose a folder on your device, app saves automatically
- **Sync via cloud** - Put auto-save folder in Dropbox/iCloud/Google Drive (you control sync, not us!)

**We NEVER see your data. Ever.** Zero-data-host architecture means your data never touches our servers.

**More:** [docs/security_privacy/privacy_model.md](docs/security_privacy/privacy_model.md)

