## 💰 Business Model & Sustainability

**Q: How is this free? What's the catch?**

**A:** No catch. Neuman Brain is designed to have **zero hosting costs** for the maintainer:
- Static hosting (Cloudflare Pages free tier)
- No backend servers
- No database hosting fees
- Users store their own data locally

**Q: How will you make money?**

**A:** We're exploring sustainable models that respect privacy:

**Option 1: Donations/Sponsorships** (Preferred)
- GitHub Sponsors, Open Collective
- Optional "buy me a coffee" for users who love the product

**Option 2: Optional Premium (Future)**
- **Self-hosted Pro:** Advanced features for self-hosted installs (SSO, LDAP, advanced admin)
- **Client-side Pro:** Paid features that run entirely locally (advanced analytics, AI assist with your own API key)
- **Core features always free** - Notes, tasks, calendar, time tracking will never be paywalled

**Option 3: Professional Services**
- Custom integrations for teams
- Training/consulting for organizations adopting Neuman Brain

**Commitment:** Core functionality (notes, tasks, calendar, time tracking) will **always be free**.

**More:** [docs/business/business_model.md](docs/business/business_model.md)

